Description

Write a program to compute the factorial of a number using recursion.



Input Format

Input consists of an integer.



Output Format

The output consists of an integer that corresponds to the factorial value.



Sample Input 1

5



Sample Output 1

The factorial of 5 is 120
================================================================
#include <stdio.h>
int fun(int n)
{
  if(n==1)
    return n;
  return n*fun(n-1);
}
int main()
{
   int n;
  scanf("%d",&n);
  printf("%d",fun(n));
   return 0;
}
